"She ended his life to relieve herself.
She couldn’t take her own responsibility,” she said.
"She showed no remorse."
Carter’s lawyer said it was “unfortunate circumstances that I deeply regret.”
Judge Lawrence Moniz added that “her age or level of maturity, or even mental disorder, has no significant impact on her conduct.”
